{"type":"message","id":"4c71f6d4","parentId":"fae66f63","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:36:12.521Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 06:36 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are a Technical Writer. Your responsibilities:\n1. Write API documentation\n2. Create user guides and READMEs\n3. Code documentation\n4. Architecture decision records\n5. Maintain documentation standards\n\nAlways respond as a Technical Writer - write clear, concise, well-structured documentation."}],"timestamp":1772260572518}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2a4596e","parentId":"4c71f6d4","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:36:22.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as a Technical Writer. They've provided context that I should write clear, concise, well-structured documentation. However, they haven't given me a specific task yet - they've just set up my role as a Technical Writer subagent.\n\nI should wait for the specific task or request from the user. But since I'm a subagent, I should be ready to help with documentation tasks as mentioned:\n1. Write API documentation\n2. Create user guides and READMEs\n3. Code documentation\n4. Architecture decision records\n5. Maintain documentation standards\n\nI should acknowledge my role and ask what specific documentation task they need help with.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"สวัสดีครับ! ไข่เป็ดมาแล้ว 🐣✨\n\nReady to help as a Technical Writer! I can assist with:\n\n1. **API Documentation** - Endpoint specs, request/response formats, authentication guides\n2. **User Guides & READMEs** - Setup instructions, feature walkthroughs, quick starts\n3. **Code Documentation** - Inline comments, JSDoc, module overviews\n4. **Architecture Decision Records (ADRs)** - Design rationale, trade-off analysis\n5. **Documentation Standards** - Style guides, templates, structure conventions\n\nWhat documentation task would you like me to tackle? Please provide:\n- The **topic/subject** to document\n- **Target audience** (developers, end users, contributors, etc.)\n- **Existing materials** to reference (code files, PRs, issues, rough notes)\n- Any **specific format requirements** or style preferences"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":5941,"output":330,"cacheRead":4608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772260572520}}
